ine Learning models cannot efficiently understand text usernames directly.\n","\n","So preprocessing converted users into numeric IDs like:\n","\n","```python\n","Original User → Encoded ID\n","\n","Raghu         → 1045\n","John          → 622\n","David         → 17\n","Priya         → 888\n","```\n","\n","This process is called:\n","\n","# 🧠 Label Encoding / User Encoding\n","\n","Machine Learning models work faster and better with numbers.\n","\n","---\n","\n","# 🚀 What happened when you entered `1045` ?\n","\n","Your system performed the following steps:\n","\n","```python\n","Find all purchases/reviews/history\n","belonging to user 1045\n","```\n","\n","Then:\n","\n","```python\n","Analyze products bought/viewed/reviewed\n","by that user\n","```\n","\n","Then:\n","\n","```python\n","Compare those products with all products\n","using TF-IDF + Cosine Similarity\n","```\n","\n","Then:\n","\n","```python\n","Recommend similar products\n","```\n","\n","---\n","\n","# 🚀 What does this line mean?\n","\n","```python\n","🧠 Total Purchases Found: 10\n","```\n","\n","This means:\n","\n","```python\n","User 1045 has 10 product records\n","inside the dataset\n","```\n","\n","Example:\n","\n","| User | Purchased Product |\n","| ---- | ----------------- |\n","| 1045 | USB Cable         |\n","| 1045 | Charger           |\n","| 1045 | Type C Cable      |\n","| 1045 | Power Bank        |\n","\n","etc...\n","\n","---\n","\n","# 🚀 What are these recommendation results?\n","\n","Example:\n","\n","| recommended product  | score |\n","| -------------------- | ----- |\n","| Flix Micro USB Cable | 1.0   |\n","| pTron Cable          | 0.91  |\n","\n","This means:\n","\n","```python\n","System thinks user 1045\n","may like these products\n","```\n","\n","based on:\n","\n","* previous purchases\n","* similar product descriptions\n","* similar keywords\n","* TF-IDF vectors\n","* cosine similarity\n","\n","---\n","\n","# 🚀 What is `score recommendation` ?\n","\n","Example:\n","\n","```python\n","1.000000\n","0.911776\n","0.677536\n","```\n","\n","This is called:\n","\n","# 🧠 Similarity Score\n","\n","Range:\n","\n","```python\n","0 → not similar\n","1 → exactly similar\n","```\n","\n","---\n","\n","# 🚀 Example\n","\n","Suppose the user purchased:\n","\n","```python\n","Micro USB Cable\n","```\n","\n","Then the system recommends:\n","\n","```python\n","Another Micro USB Cable\n","```\n","\n","because both product descriptions are very similar.\n","\n","So the similarity score becomes:\n","\n","```python\n","1.0\n","```\n","\n","---\n","\n","# 🚀 Why are some products repeated?\n","\n","You observed:\n","\n","```python\n","Flix Micro Usb Cable For Smartphone\n","```\n","\n","multiple times.\n","\n","Because your current logic:\n","\n","```python\n","similarity_scores = sorted(...)\n","```\n","\n","does NOT remove duplicate product names.\n","\n","It only removes already purchased row indices.\n","\n","So multiple rows may contain:\n","\n","* same product\n","* different reviews\n","* different sellers\n","* duplicate entries\n","\n","---\n","\n","# 🚀 Internal ML Recommendation Pipeline Flow\n","\n","```python\n","User ID (1045)\n","        ↓\n","Find user purchase history\n","        ↓\n","Convert products to TF-IDF vectors\n","        ↓\n","Cosine similarity calculation\n","        ↓\n","Rank most similar products\n","        ↓\n","Return Top 5 recommendations\n","```\n","\n","---\n","\n","# 🚀 ML Concepts Used in This Project\n","\n","You actually implemented:\n","\n","✅ Recommendation System\n","\n","✅ Content-Based Filtering\n","\n","✅ TF-IDF Vectorization\n","\n","✅ Cosine Similarity\n","\n","✅ NLP Text Feature Extraction\n","\n","✅ User-Based Recommendation Flow\n","\n","✅ Product Similarity Engine\n","\n","These are real-world Data Science and Machine Learning concepts 🚀🔥\n"],"metadata":{"id":"StzcNMo9QqVI"}},{"cell_type":"code","source":[],"metadata":{"id":"zR02Zn-CQcrV"},"execution_count":null,"outputs":[]},{"cell_type":"markdown","source":["👋 Hel